query:
INSERT INTO item_event (item_id, event_type_id, occurred_at)
            VALUES (
                (
                    SELECT i.id
                    FROM item i
                    JOIN account a ON a.id = i.account_id
                    WHERE a.account_uid = $1
                    AND i.item_uid = $2
                ),
                (SELECT id FROM item_event_type WHERE name = $3),
                $4
            )
